				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/%C4%90%C3%ACnh-th%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-s%C3%A1ch/poem-rF91EB30-zT6DtZAE4A1yw">Đình thí đối sách - 廷試對策</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-c%E1%BB%91-ki%E1%BB%83m-hi%E1%BB%87u-c%C3%B4ng-b%E1%BB%99-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-lang-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-qu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99-h%E1%BB%87-minh/poem-A6qN_vao7Go6vLRVhh8KVA">Đường cố kiểm hiệu công bộ viên ngoại lang Đỗ quân mộ hệ minh - 唐故檢校工部員外郎杜君墓系銘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/H%E1%BA%A1-V%C4%A9nh-Tr%E1%BB%A5-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-gia-nghi%C3%AAm-th%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%8D/poem-h6cTcH3J-gKp09445as_Zg">Hạ Vĩnh Trụ tiến sĩ gia nghiêm thất thập thọ - 夏永拄进士家嚴七十壽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%89-v%C4%83n-quan-qu%C3%A2n-d%C4%A9-l%C3%A2m-t%E1%BA%B7c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem--7aSmm5Sn3I7FvPVGG4inQ">Hỉ văn quan quân dĩ lâm tặc cảnh, nhị thập vận - 喜聞官軍已臨賊境二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-D%E1%BA%A7n/Huy%C3%AAn-hoa/poem-uUteh_KL6nyZX0Lbtz89aA">Huyên hoa - 萱花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-D%E1%BA%A7n/author-xraflgHOfFZLZePKI11Alg">Đường Dần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/Kh%E1%BA%A9n-c%E1%BA%A7u/poem-BOjsbfHHkudHg7HGjezu5A">Khẩn cầu - 懇求</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nguy%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%E1%BB%8B-T%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9/poem-npXw02G-jERb2RSD-vXBvg">Nguyên nhật thị Tông Vũ - 元日示宗武</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B7-long-ng%C3%A2m-%C4%90%C4%83ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn-Khang-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-T%C3%A2m-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-J8iWJijhEqtotrl02orE3Q">Thuỷ long ngâm - Đăng Kiến Khang Thưởng Tâm đình - 水龍吟－登建康賞心亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Tr%C3%A0o-chi%E1%BA%BFt-t%C3%BD-ph%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-vUxGRNIkDp-YJ_YFNJQSeA">Trào chiết tý phật kỳ 1 - 嘲折臂佛其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A3i-%E1%BA%A4n-T%C3%ADn-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-vTbWJOG6ka2qt2F3MT_yAQ">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A3i-%E1%BA%A4n-T%C3%ADn-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-T0lLFTlc1932dcfP4JVr1Q">Hải Ấn Tín thiền sư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
